  "1789340": {
    "name": "Evil's Den: Forsaken Dungeon",
    "steam_appid": 1789340,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789340/extras/601212dcc80bec305fb55313b439b5c4.webp?t=1708962544\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789340/extras/601212dcc80bec305fb55313b439b5c4.poster.avif?t=1708962544\" class=\"bb_img\" width=610 height=219 /></picture></span> <br><br>Evil's Den 是一款 rogue-lite 地牢爬行者，具有程序生成的关卡，您将在其中与成群的怪物战斗，以关闭村庄教堂中打开的通往地狱的门户。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789340/extras/5ab8e0014ddd4770121abe3e9cc0ed3e.avif?t=1708962544\" width=610 height=372 /></span><br><br><strong>帮助雷德洛沃村民</strong><br>当地的牧师愚蠢地在祭坛上献了人祭。他没想到，这次恶行，竟然打开了通往魔界的大门。<br>停止从门户中涌出的怪物浪潮，帮助 Redlovo 村的居民。村民们担心自己的生命和亲人，波美拉尼亚王国也处于危险之中，如果不关闭传送门阻止敌人，他们就会威胁到整个大陆。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789340/extras/a6eff4b4bef61ca87ac8e1e3e130ec15.poster.avif?t=1708962544\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789340/extras/a6eff4b4bef61ca87ac8e1e3e130ec15.webm?t=1708962544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789340/extras/a6eff4b4bef61ca87ac8e1e3e130ec15.mp4?t=1708962544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>从死里复活</strong><br>多亏了法师的帮助，你几乎是不朽的。如果有什么东西挡住了你的路，你摔倒了，他们会在城市里用魔法复活你。所有的希望都在你身上！<br><br><i>尝试，死亡，复活，重复。</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789340/extras/b0647f9ada59fd6e9906312c90da8d41.poster.avif?t=1708962544\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789340/extras/b0647f9ada59fd6e9906312c90da8d41.webm?t=1708962544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789340/extras/b0647f9ada59fd6e9906312c90da8d41.mp4?t=1708962544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>新挑战，新地牢！</strong><br>地下城是程序生成的，这意味着您永远不会两次玩同一关卡，每次进入邪恶巢穴时都会建立新的挑战。每次运行都会略有不同，进入传送门时，期待新的挑战。<br><br><strong>抢劫！</strong><br>单手和双手剑、斧头、武士刀、盾牌、弓箭，甚至新法术。这一切都在地牢里等着你，亲爱的冒险家。获取蓝图并在城市中制造新武器，以帮助您进行下一次跑步！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789340/extras/6612dd1bf807707dbb417ffb6c053003.poster.avif?t=1708962544\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789340/extras/6612dd1bf807707dbb417ffb6c053003.webm?t=1708962544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789340/extras/6612dd1bf807707dbb417ffb6c053003.mp4?t=1708962544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>成长壮大</strong><br>您可以在下次尝试击败邪恶巢穴的领主之前使用获得的黄金重新武装。多亏了这一点，他肮脏的爪牙会给你带来更少的麻烦，你会更接近你的目标。法师会教你新法术，铁匠会根据你提供的制作配方制作武器。去战斗，成为传奇！",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 保加利亚语, 繁体中文, 简体中文, 捷克语, 丹麦语, 芬兰语, 希腊语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 荷兰语, 日语, 韩语, 挪威语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 罗马尼亚语, 瑞典语, 泰语, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语, 越南语, 匈牙利语, 印度尼西亚语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
